                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6616" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1030</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10697 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">逆势增长，渠道为王：良品铺子疫情下的全渠道建设</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Counter trend growth, channel is king: all channel construction under the epidemic situation of the BESTORE</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">曹麒麟，左仁淑，杨丽芳，苟清鑫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">四川大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">良品铺子股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">食品工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">渠道管理；全渠道；新冠疫情；良品铺子；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Channel Management; Omni Channel;  COVID-19; the BESTORE</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年初，新冠疫情爆发，在我国传统零售行业受到巨大冲击之际，良品铺子却逆势上扬，高光“云上市”。本案例详细回顾了良品铺子的成长历程，描述了良品铺子从传统的线下实体连锁店转战线上销售，并利用数字化赋能实施多渠道建设，近年来依托自有渠道网络，结合热点事件、网红直播等形式开展多维度全渠道营销的创新之路。案例还深入剖析了良品铺子在不同时期面临的主要问题以及应对策略，从中我们可以看到，全渠道建设帮助企业扩大市场、提升效率，数字化赋能有效打通渠道壁垒，解决客户痛点，最终构建起以顾客为中心的营销体系。多年的积累加上疫情期间的及时调整，成为良品铺子应对疫情危机逆势增长的实力之策。良品铺子的发展经验，对于休闲食品行业，甚至是整个零售行业都有指导和借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">At the beginning of 2020, the COVID-19 broke out. When China&#39;s traditional retail industry was greatly impacted, the BESTORE rose against the trend and &quot;went public in the cloud&quot;. This case reviews the growth process of the BESTORE in detail, and describes the innovation road of the BESTORE from traditional offline physical chain stores to online sales, and uses digital empowerment to implement multi-channel construction. In recent years, relying on its own channel network, it has carried out multi-dimensional Omni channel marketing in the form of hot events and online celebrity live broadcast. The case also deeply analyzes the main problems and Countermeasures Faced by the BESTORE in different periods, from which we can see that the omni channel construction helps enterprises expand the market and improve efficiency, digital empowerment effectively breaks through channel barriers, solves customer pain points, and finally builds a customer-centered marketing system. Years of accumulation and timely adjustment during the epidemic period have become the strength strategy for the BESTORE to cope with the adverse growth of the epidemic crisis. The development experience of the BESTORE can be used as a guide and reference for the leisure food industry and even the whole retail industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《营销管理》、《渠道管理》、《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">全渠道零售；零售渠道演化路径；全渠道零售过程；企业数字化转型与渠道管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
